{"title":"Draft MGN 554 Consutlation - Marine Equipment Directive - UK Applicant Notified Bodies","public_updated_at":"2016-10-31T11:33:46Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This consultation is for a new Marine Guidance Note (MGN) which sets out the process for a Conformity Assessment Body (CAB) seeking status as a UK Notified Body (NB) in accordance with Directive 2014/90/EU on marine equipment (the Marine Equipment Directive). This Guidance note also forms one of the administrative instruments which transpose the Marine Equipment Directive in the UK.</p>\n\n<p>Any responses should be clearly labelled as “Consultation – Applicant Notified Bodies”. Please include the name of the company you represent, as applicable and give any feedback or comments you have on the draft MGN to the below email address.</p>\n</div>","closing_date":"2016-09-09T23:45:00.000+01:00","emphasised_organisations":["23a24aa8-1711-42b6-bf6b-47af0f230295"],"opening_date":"2016-08-19T12:00:00.000+01:00","change_history":[{"public_timestamp":"2016-10-31T11:33:46.000+00:00","note":"Consultation responses published"},{"public_timestamp":"2016-08-19T12:00:00.000+01:00","note":"First published."}],"documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1783978\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/546945/Consultation_Letter_-_Applicant_NB.pdf\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/546945/thumbnail_Consultation_Letter_-_Applicant_NB.pdf.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a aria-describedby=\"attachment-1783978-accessibility-help\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/546945/Consultation_Letter_-_Applicant_NB.pdf\">Consultee Information Letter</a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\"